RECIPE
+Make bananas brown
+Peel & wrap in saran wrap & put in freezer
+One day later, take out of freezer, leave for 1 minute. Then slice into 1/2 inch slices
+Using double boiler, melt chocolate
+dip frozen slices into melted chocolate and put on prepared cookie sheet with wax paper
+Put back in freezer for 15-30 minutes

+ENJOY!

